<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="easily-adv">easily <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'iːzəli/    美 /'iːzəli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>容易地；不费力地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Fortune is easily found, but hard to be kept.
聚财容易，守财难。/幸福易寻难维持。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You <strong>could easily</strong> add to your happiness with more love.
拥有更多的爱就有可能增添几分快乐。</p><footer>2014 福建</footer></div></div>